text: Kathey Lichty (born 16 October 1957) is a Canadian rower. She competed in the women's eight event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Canada Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from North Bay, Ontario
